# Booting your watch (DX2/DX3) into the developer menu.
(this isnt needed, this is just a guide to see and test stuff)

1. Turn off master switch.
2. Hold Camera and Home button.
3. Turn on master switch
4. Rapidly start tapping on your screen.
5. You should be in the dev menu.

To exit just click the home button on the main menu.
